": \"two hours\", \"from\": 188, \"to\": 197}, {\"ngram\": \"51 minutes\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 209}, {\"ngram\": \"three seconds\", \"from\": 214, \"to\": 227}, {\"ngram\": \"her finish\", \"from\": 240, \"to\": 250}, {\"ngram\": \"the final day\", \"from\": 261, \"to\": 274}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 278, \"to\": 296}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Harvey has now taken toInstagramto reveal the 'heartbreaking' news of her leg break, and how she did not let it stop her from fulfilling her Olympic dream in Paris.\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 457, \"end\": 462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999948854112, \"rank\": 5.1145890667933096e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Harvey\", \"from\": 299, \"to\": 305}, {\"ngram\": \"toInstagramto\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 333}, {\"ngram\": \"the 'heartbreaking' news\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 365}, {\"ngram\": \"her leg break\", \"from\": 369, \"to\": 382}, {\"ngram\": \"her Olympic dream\", \"from\": 436, \"to\": 453}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'This was far from the Olympics I dreamed of, but still an experience of a lifetime,' Great Britain's Olympic star Harvey posted, with a picture of herself on crutches.\", \"from\": 465, \"to\": 633, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 580, \"end\": 586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Harvey\", \"score\": 0.9989603592887549, \"rank\": 0.0006713034019561958, \"text\": \"Harvey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Harvey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Neil_Harvey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 496}, {\"ngram\": \"still an experience\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 534}, {\"ngram\": \"a lifetime\", \"from\": 538, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"Britain's Olympic star\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 579}, {\"ngram\": \"a picture\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 609}, {\"ngram\": \"crutches\", \"from\": 624, \"to\": 632}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I was so excited to step on that stage, show that I had what it takes to be part of Team GB and most importantly, do everyone proud who has helped me get to this point.\", \"from\": 635, \"to\": 804, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 720, \"end\": 727, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999898768890834, \"rank\": 6.737250374853881e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that stage\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 674}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 716}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 753, \"to\": 761}, {\"ngram\": \"this point\", \"from\": 793, \"to\": 803}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And just a couple of weeks ago, it was looking so good.\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 862, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"weeks\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 833}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Training had been stellar.\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 889, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Training\", \"from\": 863, \"to\": 871}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then I developed a bit of tightness in my hip.\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 907, \"to\": 912}, {\"ngram\": \"tightness\", \"from\": 916, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"my hip\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 935}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'My incredible team and I put in so much work to make the start line fit and healthy, and we were all optimistic that with a bit of race day adrenaline I would be able to run the race I knew I had in me.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1141, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"'My incredible team\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 957}, {\"ngram\": \"so much work\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"the start\", \"from\": 992, \"to\": 1001}, {\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1061, \"to\": 1066}, {\"ngram\": \"race day\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1078}, {\"ngram\": \"adrenaline\", \"from\": 1079, \"to\": 1089}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1113, \"to\": 1121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'A couple of miles in, I quickly realised that wasn't going to happen.\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1213, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"miles\", \"from\": 1156, \"to\": 1161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The next 24 miles were a painful battle.\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The next 24 miles\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"a painful battle\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It turns out I had stress fractured my femur.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"stress\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1280}, {\"ngram\": \"my femur\", \"from\": 1291, \"to\": 1299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'In any other race, I would have stopped and there were so many moments when I thought I could not take another step.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any other race\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1320}, {\"ngram\": \"so many moments\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"another step\", \"from\": 1406, \"to\": 1418}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The downhills were hell.\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1444, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The downhills\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"hell\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1443}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But despite that most of my race goals having slipped away, there was still a tiny part of my Olympic dream that I could hang on to - and that was finishing the Olympic marathon.\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1625, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my race goals\", \"from\": 1472, \"to\": 1485}, {\"ngram\": \"a tiny part\", \"from\": 1523, \"to\": 1534}, {\"ngram\": \"my Olympic dream\", \"from\": 1538, \"to\": 1554}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic marathon\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1624}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I could not give up.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1648, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I kept telling myself to smile, soak up the energy of the incredible crowds and just put one foot in front of the other.\", \"from\": 1649, \"to\": 1769, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the energy\", \"from\": 1689, \"to\": 1699}, {\"ngram\": \"the incredible crowds\", \"from\": 1703, \"to\": 1724}, {\"ngram\": \"one foot\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 1750, \"to\": 1755}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was heartbreaking.\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1793, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But being part of the Olympics is something I will never forget and being able to share the race with so many of my amazing friends and family meant the world to me.'\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1804, \"to\": 1808}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1824}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1828, \"to\": 1837}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"my amazing friends\", \"from\": 1907, \"to\": 1925}, {\"ngram\": \"family\", \"from\": 1930, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1952}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ArrowMORE:Team GB star Adam Peaty makes retirement decision after Paris Olympics ArrowMORE:Russia says Paris Olympics' closing ceremony was 'obvious Satanism' ArrowMORE:JK Rowling and Elon Musk named in Imane Khelif 'cyber harassment' lawsuit after Olympics win Punchy analysis, transfer talk and more from Metro's football experts, sent straight to your inbox every week.\", \"from\": 1964, \"to\": 2339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1987, \"end\": 1997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia